          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2017-06-26T19:55:39Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Veterans Education Improvement Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill permits veterans to use Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) Post-9/11 educational assistance for an accredited independent study program offered by an educational institution that is not an institution of higher learning, such as an area career and technical education school or a postsecondary vocational institution providing postsecondary level education.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2017-06-14T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
        </item>
